# Product wiki — Connected product

Internal reference document for customer support and the virtual agent.  
Company: **Entreprise SAS** — B2B and B2C sales.

---

## 1. Company overview

Entreprise SAS designs and sells **connected products** for consumers and businesses.  
Shipped from France (standard delivery 3 to 5 business days depending on destination).

- **Website**: www.entreprise.example (demo)
- **Support**: support@entreprise.example — Mon.–Fri. 9 a.m.–6 p.m. (CET)
- **Phone**: +33 1 84 00 00 00 (main line, callback within 24 h)
- **Legal warranty**: 2 years (consumer); business terms on quote

